y</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_Čerm."/><biblScope>134</biblScope></bibl></cit></cit><etym xml:lang="ru">Из %iæ-fælmon%i, где <xr><ref target="#entry_æ-"/></xr> — негативная частица, а %ifælmon%i (отдельно не употребляется) восходит к <mentioned xml:lang="x-oldirn"><lang/><w>*pari-man</w></mentioned> от %iman%i- ‘думать’, ‘заботиться’ и пр.; ср. <mentioned xml:lang="xpr"><lang/><w>*parmāng(prmʽng)</w><gloss><q>мысль</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl corresp="#ref_SPAW"><biblScope>1934, стр. 905</biblScope></bibl>). Тот же корень %iman%i- ‘думать’ в другом сложении находим в <mentioned xml:lang="os"><lang/><w>fæsmon</w><gloss><q>раскаяние</q></gloss></mentioned> q. v. Ср. также <xr><ref target="#entry_amond"/><ref target="#entry_monc"/><ref target="#entry_mondag"/></xr>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">From %iæ-fælmon%i, where <xr><ref target="#entry_æ-"/></xr> is a negative particle and %ifælmon%i (is not used separately) ttraces back to <mentioned xml:lang="x-oldirn"><lang/><w>*pari-man</w></mentioned> from %iman%i- ‘to think’, ‘to care’ etc.; compare <mentioned xml:lang="xpr"><lang/><w>*parmāng(prmʽng)</w><gloss><q>thought</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl corresp="#ref_SPAW"><biblScope>1934, стр. 905</biblScope></bibl>). The same root %iman%i- ‘to think’ is found in <mentioned xml:lang="os"><lang/><w>fæsmon</w><gloss><q>repentance</q></gloss></mentioned> q. v. Compare also <xr><ref target="#entry_amond"/><ref target="#entry_monc"/><ref target="#entry_mondag"/></xr>.</etym></entry>